        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "AS YOU TAUGHT TORAH\nto those whose names I bear,\nteach me Torah, too.\nIts mystery beckons,\nyet I struggle with its truth.\nYou meant Torah for me:\ndid You mean the struggle for me, too?\nDon't let me struggle alone;\nhelp me\nto understand,\nto be wise, to listen, to know...\nLead me into the mystery.\nבָּרוּךְ אַתָּה, יְיָ, אוֹהֵב עַמּוֹ יִשְׂרָאֵל.\nBaruch atah, Adonai, ohev amo Yisrael.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-14T19:52:18.214Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "KQMbuYqx1n5EXi9HO_Ke"
      },
